                  <strong>Most recent federal tax return (Form 1040) — full copy</strong>
                  <p>Include all pages and schedules. Download from IRS.gov if you cannot locate your copy.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="doc-item">
                <div class="doc-check">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>W-2s and 1099s for the most recent tax year</strong>
                  <p>All income statements showing wages, contract income, or investment income.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="doc-item">
                <div class="doc-check">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Tax returns for the 2 prior years (recommended)</strong>
                  <p>Demonstrates income stability over time. Consular officers may request these even if not initially required.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="doc-cat">
            <div class="doc-cat-header">
