                  <strong>Brokerage / investment account statements</strong>
                  <p>Most recent statement showing current market value of all holdings.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="doc-item">
                <div class="doc-check">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Retirement account statements (IRA, 401k)</strong>
                  <p>Current balance statements. Note that early withdrawal penalties may reduce the effective value officers will consider.</p>
                </div>
